<p>
  A real-time character counter appears near the input box showing <code>current/maximum</code>
  (e.g., <code>127/1000</code>).
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_palette}>Color Indicators</.help_h4>
<p>
  The counter changes color as you approach the limit:<br /><strong>Green</strong>
  — under 80% used<br /><strong>Orange</strong>
  — 80-95% used<br /><strong>Red</strong>
  — over 95% used
</p>
